    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this superlative vehicle, preserved in showroom condition. This unit has been meticulously curated, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in pristine, original state. Every mechanical component has been subjected to a rigorous inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards of performance and reliability. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of uncompromising quality and distinguished pedigree.",
      "price": 46500.0,
