    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83c\udf1f I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells brand new! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it\u2019s been garage-kept and meticulously maintained. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or speck of wear on this beauty. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure. Come see it for yourself, I promise you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
