      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3 that serves as a masterclass in atmospheric induction. This example features the legendary S54 straight-six, with the critical rod bearing service and double-VANOS system overhaul fully documented. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, while the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, complemented by a pristine M Variable Differential Lock for precise torque vectoring. With original paint depth and an interior devoid of typical bolster wear, this is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
